830
00:49:40,281 --> 00:49:43,241
[laughing]

831
00:49:45,939 --> 00:49:47,767
CALAMITA:
You think you're so smart?

832
00:49:47,941 --> 00:49:50,422
Let's see how smart...

833
00:49:50,596 --> 00:49:53,642
