886
00:53:52,229 --> 00:53:53,578
-[door opens]
-[bell jingles]

887
00:53:53,752 --> 00:53:55,667
[sniffles]

888
00:53:57,669 --> 00:53:59,497
-[door closes]
-[bell jingles]

889
00:54:09,594 --> 00:54:11,160
-[door opens]
-[bell jingles]

890
